<plot>The prophecies of Nostradamus, written hundreds of years ago, are interpreted as predicting certain post-World War II events. These include the ascension of 'Queen Elizabeth II' (qv) to the throne of England, the creation of the United Nations, the Korean War, atomic bomb testing, the trials of Communist spies in the early 1950s, and new ways that astronomers will study the universe.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?400972</url></doc>
